## 5. NAVIGATION ARCHITECTURE (how routing works)

- Root `app/_layout.tsx` provides global providers (Theme, i18n, OTA overlay) and renders `<Stack />` from Expo Router.
- The `<Stack>` navigator uses `app/(stack)/_layout.tsx` as its configuration.
- The home screen is `app/(stack)/index.tsx`.
- All other screens are defined in `app/(stack)/_layout.tsx` as named routes.
- No tabs, no drawer — pure stack navigation with swipe‑back and optional modal presentations.

